gobblin.data.management.conversion.hive.watermarker

Interface HiveSourceWatermarker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PartitionLevelWatermarker, TableLevelWatermarker

    public interface HiveSourceWatermarker
    An interface to read previous high watermarks and write new high watermarks to state.
